41. Write a program to find the sum of digits of N digit number (sum should 
be single digit) 
Sample Input: 
Enter N value : 3 
Enter 3 digit number: 143 
Sample Output: 
Sum of  3 digit number: 8 

CODE: 
public class SumOfDigits {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        int n = 3;       // number of digits
        int num = 143;   // the N-digit number

        int sum = 0;

        // keep summing until single digit
        while (num > 9) {
            sum = 0;
            while (num > 0) {
                sum += num % 10;
                num /= 10;
            }
            num = sum;
        }

        System.out.println("Sum of " + n + " digit number: " + num);
    }
}
